 toad (Atelopus halihelos) in Ecuador is listed as critically endangered.\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/10/04/Atelopus-halihelos-frogs-study.png?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=810\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1440\" /></div><figcaption class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-caption\">The Morona-Santiago stubfoot toad (Atelopus halihelos) in Ecuador is listed as critically endangered. <span class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-credit\">Jaime Culebras/Photo Wildlife Tours</span></figcaption></figure><p>Two out of five amphibians are currently threatened with extinction. </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com/environment/amphibians-climate-change-conservation/\" rel=\"nof", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/environment/amphibians-climate-change-conservation/", "date_published": "2023-10-04T15:00:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead": null, "artist": "Popular Science", "album": "Popular Science", "user": null, "language": "en-US", "thumbnail": "https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2021/04/28/cropped-PSC3.png?auto=webp&width=32&height=32"}, {"source": "https://www.popsci.com/feed", "title": "This robot trio mimics the life cycle of a frog", "description": "<figure class=\"Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--hasCaption\">\n                    <div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper\"><img alt=\"Four legged robot inspired by frog\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/10/04/Zhao-robot-colorado-state-1-1024x763-1.png?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=810\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1440\" /></div><figcaption class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-caption\">The robots are inspired by frogs' multiple life stages. <span class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-credit\"><a href=\"https://engr.source.colostate.edu/morphing-robots-designed-at-csu-can-grip-climb-and-crawl-like-insects/\">Colorado State University</a></span></figcaption></figure><p>Search-and-rescue operations could one day feature a fleet of frog-bots to help save the day.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com/environment/frog-robot-trio-video", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/environment/frog-robot-trio-video/", "date_published": "2023-10-04T14:00:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead": null, "artist": "Popular Science", "album": "Popular Science", "user": null, "language": "en-US", "thumbnail": "https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2021/04/28/cropped-PSC3.png?auto=webp&width=32&height=32"}, {"source": "https://www.popsci.com/feed", "title": "Discoverers of colorful quantum dot nanotech win 2023 Nobel Prize in chemistry", "description": "<figure class=\"Article-thumbnail orgnc-SingleImage orgnc-SingleImage--center orgnc-SingleImage--hasCaption\">\n                    <div class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-wrapper\"><img alt=\"Moungi Bawendi, Louis Brus, and Alexei Ekimov will share the 2023 Nobel prize in chemistry.\" class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-image webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.popsci.com/uploads/2023/10/04/nobel-chemistry-prize-2023.png?auto=webp&amp;width=1440&amp;height=810\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1440\" /></div><figcaption class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-caption\">Moungi Bawendi, Louis Brus, and Alexei Ekimov will share the 2023 Nobel prize in chemistry. <span class=\"orgnc-SingleImage-credit\">Niklas Elmehed/Nobel Prize Outreach </span></figcaption></figure><p>Quantum dots can be found in modern computers, televisions, LED lights, and more. </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.popsci.com/science/nobel-prize-chemistry-quantum-dots/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discoverers", "link": "https://www.popsci.com/science/nobel-prize-chemistry-quantum-dots/", "date_published": "2023-10-04T13:00:00+00:00", "bookmarked": false, "dead":